com.viaoa.object

Class OAObjectTestDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.object.OAObjectTestDelegate

  • public class OAObjectTestDelegate
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to "offer" services for testing the OAObject using Test Data objects from the test package. The idea is to have the Data objects match the changes in OAObject and then to compare the results to make sure that everything matches.
    Author:
    vincevia
